   @ 170, 10  SAY "Line width:"  SIZE 90, 22

   @ 16, 36 COMBOBOX oCombo1 ITEMS aPenStyles SIZE 120, 24 STYLE CBS_DROPDOWNLIST + WS_TABSTOP

   @ 170, 36 EDITBOX oEdit1 CAPTION "" SIZE 32, 24

